{"tid":361553,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國新移民　一年55,700人　持單程證湧港　每日唔止150個","createTime":"2017-08-16T08:24:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-16T09:23:58.000Z","uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a2f54ee66c384a4d282894bbd27e8b640f24d557","tid":361553,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T08:24:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170810/57065019\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170810%2F57065019&d=KvtloBbkJC6H0RGqyDvczCwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=bd2cdf55\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170810%2F57065019&h=e3726d7d\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170810/57065019</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170810/large/1502364670_2e25.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170810%2Flarge%2F1502364670_2e25.png&h=0f848200&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n政府統計處發表最新人口數字，2017年年中香港人口的臨時數字為7,389,500人，與去年同期比較，增加52,900人，增長率為0.7%。<br />\n<br />\n統計處表示，人口增展由自然增長，亦即出生減死亡人數，以及香港居民淨遷移，亦即移入減移出人數所組成。2016年年中至2017年年中的人口自然增長為14,300人，其中出生人數為59,600人，死亡人數為45,300人；同期淨遷移人數為38,600人，其中55,700人為「單程證持有人」的移入，17,100人為其他香港居民的淨移出。<br />\n按一年365日計算，平均每日有超過152名單程證持有人，移入香港。"},{"pid":"3394ba3eb0398c5cb57750f858840d9311da63fb","tid":361553,"uid":41245,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T08:29:33.000Z","msg":"依班人你唔散播港獨思想畀佢<br />\n佢就會俾保蝗搶咗<br />\n事實見到最多蝗嘅天水圍<br />\n本土支持人口係最多<br />\n依個只係事實，冇任何意思<br />\n人就入咗嚟，點教化佢地係我地嘅責任<br />\n失敗主義只係叛國，講出嚟只係維穩"},{"pid":"82987431e856a57348db3827e95727c7a27131f0","tid":361553,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T09:23:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}